message.content: ∀ (r : ℝ), 0 < r → Filter.Tendsto (fun r => inf {abs (r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)) | m n : ℤ}) Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → (∃ (m n : ℤ), IsLeast (Set.Icc 0 (|r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)|)) (G r)) → Filter.Tendsto (G) Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (r : ℝ),
  (∀ m n : ℤ, G r = min (abs (r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)))) →
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (hG : ∀ r, G r = ⨅ (m n : ℤ), |r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)|),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ {G : ℝ → ℝ} (r : ℝ),
  (∀ m n : ℤ, G r = min G r |r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)|) →
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (r : ℝ), (∀ m n : ℤ, G r = |r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)|) → Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (hG : ∀ r, G r = (Set.univ : Set ℤ × ℤ).Inf (fun ⟨m, n⟩ => |r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)|)),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ) (r : ℝ),
  (∀ (m n : ℤ), G r ≤ |r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)|) →
    Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
Theorem exists_limit_eq_zero : ∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ), (∀ r : ℝ, 0 < r → (∃ m n : ℤ, G r = |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2)|)) → Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0) := sorry.
